Whereas Afghanistan’s Independent Election Commission has
			 affirmed that Afghanistan will hold presidential and provincial elections in
			 April 2014 and parliamentary elections in 2015;

Whereas security concerns and voter intimidation have
			 impeded the ability of people in Afghanistan to cast votes reliably and safely
			 in past elections;

Whereas the Honorable Hamid Karzai is the first
			 democratically elected president of modern Afghanistan and has served two terms
			 in that position;

